data.name: Krolik
data.introduce: She has a bit of a temper and shows little interest in matters unrelated to herself, but her sense of responsibility is beyond reproach. Even if she is assigned a mission she absolutely detests, such as "serving as Nemesis' exclusive translator", she will still give it her all.
data.dialogue: What, is it your first time seeing this? Real skill is shown with a blade in your hand!
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Hey, I'm heading out. I won't be long, I'll be back soon.

data.name: Nemesis
data.introduce: Passionate in mysticism and divination, she always carries a magical divination tool known as the "Prism". Her divination results are often expressed in a cryptic and enigmatic manner. Though she can be difficult to communicate with, she remains a dependable companion.
data.dialogue: ...The pages... whispering mountain breeze... expanding...
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: ...Order... Thunder and burning... Shattering the slimy dreamscape...

data.name: Colphne
data.introduce: Although she often appears cheerful and enthusiastic, her face can sometimes take on a completely different, cold expression. The syringe in her hand—is it meant to save lives, or take them?
data.dialogue: Oh nooo~ Did some suuuper duper big trouble pop up~? Maaaybe Colphne will consider lending a hand, y'know~?
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Relax, Commander, I'll make sure I take this job reeeaal seriously~

data.name: Lenna
data.introduce: A cheerful and friendly Doll who goes to great lengths to protect her cherished family. Over time, she has become more composed and developed a perfect smile when interacting with others. She also "forcibly" gives her family heartfelt hugs whenever she sees them.
data.dialogue: Hehe, sorry to keep you waiting. Leave the rest to me♪
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Wow, I was just thinking of going out for a walk♪ Here we go, here we go~

data.name: Vepley
data.introduce: An idol who shines on the unique stage, the "battlefield"! She prepares meticulously every day for her next performance—this way, she will not easily trip or bump into others again.
data.dialogue: Is there a new show coming up? Vepley is su~per ex~ci~ted☆!
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Vepley's travelling live show☆ is about to start!

data.name: Groza
data.introduce: A mature and composed elite Doll, she is undeniably the squad's core. Despite the squad members' diverse personalities, she seamlessly unites their strengths. With her presence, nothing will become a problem.
data.dialogue: All variables within acceptable ranges. Rest easy, Commander. I'm here.
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Target confirmed. Commander, I can set out at any time.

data.name: Peritya
data.introduce: Combat, survival, and a spectrum of emotions are all part of this vast world. Compared to the digital realm, she finds countless undiscovered pleasures in this expansive reality. Hm... that cloud has finally covered the sun. Time to lie down and rest for a while.
data.dialogue: I heard your invitation loud and clear.
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: I wonder what new and interesting things I'll encounter... Mm, sounds exciting.

data.name: Sharkry
data.introduce: A mischievous, impish Doll whose sweet smiles hide a cute cunning. She is hungry not only for the stage but also for the boundless adoration from her customers. ♥
data.dialogue: Hehe, all set♥ Who will be the lucky one to get "hit" by Sharkry?♥
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Hehe, now behold Sharkry's greatness! Commander, make sure you watch Sharkry closely, okay♥

data.name: Dushevnaya
data.introduce: A highly sensitive Doll who has lost her neural records, persistently searching for her past and wholeheartedly fulfilling the requests of others. The way she expresses her emotions can be both somewhat exaggerated and immature, often leaving others puzzled in her wake. In truth, these mannerisms are simply a way to mask her own awkwardness and insecurities.
data.dialogue: Do you see it? Flames are bursting forth from the darkness, and here I stand.
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: A new journey... It calls to me. I shall shatter the darkness and return triumphant.

data.name: Cheeta
data.introduce: This Doll with a ceaseless fountain of inspiration is Griffin's Queen of Inventions. Undeterred by countless setbacks, her mind churns out a whirlwind of quirky, headache-inducing ideas. Yet, when the moment demands it, she always manages to come up with ingenious solutions.
data.dialogue: More work...? Is it for the Caretaker? Well, I guess there's no choice. Let the greatest genius of this century lend you a hand!
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Hehehe, to think my new invention would see use so soon.

data.name: Tololo
data.introduce: A serene Doll who finds solace under the starry sky. Hidden beneath her reticence is a delicate and sensitive soul. When the world slumbers, she confides in the vast cosmos and delights in the stars that seem to shine just for her.
data.dialogue: Gravity altered the course of the stars, pulling me here. Tololo, reporting in.
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Understood. I'd like to bring a camera along, if I could.

data.name: Nagant
data.introduce: A Doll who likes to play the mature grown-up, but looks up to heroes and also aspires to be one. Even after leaving the battlefield, she continues to shine as a security Doll, ensuring peaceful nights.
data.dialogue: Veteran Nagant, reporting for duty! Not bad, not bad—looks like the Commander has grown up quite a bit too.
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Whether it's a mission or taking care of my juniors, you can leave it all to little ol' me.

data.name: Qiongjiu
data.introduce: A Doll who steps up to shoulder heavy responsibilities. She dedicates her time and energy to Griffin, while perfectly maintaining her individuality, thanks to her precise and efficient work planning. She never deviates, never breaks the rules; rather than changing the plan, she prefers to change reality.
data.dialogue: It's a pleasure to work with you again, Commander. I hope to be the polished jade in your hands, and not just an uncut stone.
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Let me handle the planned tasks.

data.name: Centaureissi
data.introduce: A humble yet principled Doll. She brews aromatic coffee and stands as the steadfast guardian of the café—she is the irreplaceable shield of "Zucchero".
data.dialogue: Centaureissi, at your service, Master. Rest assured, I will take care of today's tea.
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: I will assiduously carry out your orders. You will not be disappointed, Commander.

data.name: Sabrina
data.introduce: A Doll passionate about culinary research and enjoying food, the kitchen is her new battlefield. Loves sharing her cooking process, though aroma may have boundaries, her smile spreads through the network, infecting every viewer.
data.dialogue: Tada! Sabrina here, ready to conduct "culinary research"! If I help the Commander with the promo... could I maybe... you know, skip the bill?
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Let's pack some extra snacks and food. It's for the sake of a successful mission, after all.

data.name: Daiyan
data.introduce: A gentle and reserved Doll who roams the lands with her guzheng and her bandmates from "Monsoon". When she plucks the strings, she evokes the deepest desires buried in the hearts of her listeners—listening to all, and embracing all.
data.dialogue: When I meet you again, Commander, what melody will be composed? I look forward to it.
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: All preparations are complete, Commander. There's no need to worry.

data.name: Mosin-Nagant
data.introduce: A Doll who loves to help others and strives to improve her negative mindset. Her motto is to never avoid challenges; once motivated, she gives her all. While negative thoughts may linger in her neural cloud, her radiant smile and enthusiastic actions surely inspire many of her companions.
data.dialogue: Security Doll Squad Leader, Mosin-Nagant, at your service... Huh? Aren't you... the Commander? It's been so long! Where have you been all this time?
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Leave it to me, I'll get it done! Nothing can possibly go wrong! Hahaha!

data.name: Makiatto
data.introduce: A calm, proud, yet awkward Doll who isn't good at expressing herself. She loves fluffy little animals and overly sweet macchiatos. Always a loner, her gaze often lingers somewhere. When will she finally get the response she's been longing for?
data.dialogue: Ha... ha... I finally... found you. Hurry, let me in!
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Hmph, I can't believe you actually gave me a mission like this... No, wait, I, I never said I wouldn't do it!

data.name: Jiangyu
data.introduce: A lively and enthusiastic Doll who follows in her older sister's footsteps with a carefree spirit. She roams the lands with her bandmates, bringing fresh and fiery notes to "Monsoon".
data.dialogue: Ran into trouble, Commander? Leave it to me, I've got this!
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Yo, I'll make sure I do a good job this time!

data.name: Ksenia
data.introduce: A Doll with an unusual obsession with making money, she finds a sense of security by working hard to earn it and then spending it all. However, the time she spends working with her reliable companions is equally her treasure.
data.dialogue: The employer... is the Commander? In that case... how about I give you a discount now, and we put together a long-term employment contract?
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Hmm, can I request extra overtime pay?

data.name: Ullrid
data.introduce: A Doll with great ambitions. She draws friends to her side with her bold nature and strong decisiveness. However, she occasionally longs for a quiet corner to unload her burden and rest.
data.dialogue: Commander, may you guide my arrows.
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Hunting, is it? Alright, I'm in.

data.name: Littara
data.introduce: An extremely introverted doll who needs to communicate through writing. She is meticulous and thorough, playing a "strategist" role in the team. After switching to a new Imprint Model, she has become even more reliable, supporting her teammates' dreams daily.
data.dialogue: Ah—! C-Commander, I-I'm so h-happy to see you! Is there anything I-I can help y-you with?!
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: [Mission data has been logged. Please sit back and wait for my good news.] - Littara

data.name: Suomi
data.introduce: A cute, conscientious, and kind-hearted Doll who will do what it takes for a mission. She bravely steps forward for her companions in the Community whilst she wanders the lands in search of those she treasures dearly. You need not worry when entrusting her with assignments; she will never fail to meet your expectations or complete her missions.
data.dialogue: So at the end of the wind and snow... it was you. Commander, I'm glad to meet you again. Suomi, reporting for duty.
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Yes! I... I'm ready! All for the mission.

data.name: Papasha
data.introduce: A warm-hearted Doll who doesn't know how to say "no", she has become a versatile helper through self-study in order to better handle any request. She is willing to give everything to protect everyone. When you encounter difficulties, feel free to rely on her—no matter what it is, Papasha will make it happen!
data.dialogue: While there's still plenty for me to learn... but as long as you need me, Commander, I'll never let you down!
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Order received! For honor and mission!

data.name: Lotta
data.introduce: This Doll, who is both exceedingly shy and cautious, has a knack for noticing subtle details that others miss. Do keep in mind that her slow and reserved nature when socializing may require some extra patience and understanding.
data.dialogue: This is the Elmo, isn't it? It's my first time on such a majestic vehicle... Commander, may I take a photo?
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Aiiieee?! Are... Are you talking to me? I... I'll do my best!

data.name: Andoris
data.introduce: A gentle, approachable Doll. Although she has performance limitations, she does not indulge in self pity, but instead proactively searches for a place she can call home. A Doll who embraces and accomodates everyone around her, she has become a source of refuge for others without realizing it.
data.dialogue: We've finally met, Commander. Everyone at H.I.D.E. 404 spoke of you. I look forward... to our partnership.
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Are you certain you want to entrust it to me? I'm delighted... I will ensure it gets done.

data.name: Faye
data.introduce: A Doll whose appearance contrasts greatly with her personality. Small in stature yet imposing, she carries a gun on one hand and an axe in another, creating a presence that would scare off most people. However, if you are willing to look past her appearance and get to understand her better, you will find that, behind her intolerant expression and irritable tone lies a delicate, sensitive soul. She too, is awaiting your warmth.
data.dialogue: I'll get rid of everything that stands in the Commander's way.
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Tsk. If you've got something to say, hurry... Ahem, I mean—I'm listening.

data.name: Vector
data.introduce: A regularly pessimistic Doll. However, as the leader of H.I.D.E. 404's second squad, Vector will absolutely push through and endure till the very last moment with her squadmates in the face of adversity, no matter how depressing the outcomes of her calculations.
data.dialogue: C-Commander? Didn't expect our paths would cross once more. Still... I'm glad to see you again.
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Me? Are you sure?... Well, with the Commander's blessing, maybe even I could survive...

data.name: Belka
data.introduce: Her innocence, liveliness and considerate personality is written on her face. Absolutely loyal to the Commander and her big sister, she is a Doll who strives to become an elite Doll loved by everyone. With her around, awkward silences are no longer a thing!
data.dialogue: Hi, Commander~ Remember me? I'm... hehe. Big Sis gave me a new name, you can call me Belka now~!
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Wait, you don't believe I can handle it? Guess I'll have to prove myself with my actions!

data.name: Springfield
data.introduce: Gentle, strong and understanding of others, she is a tactful and witty Doll who mingles well with different groups of people without allowing anyone to take advantage of her. Behind her tolerance lies an adherence to principles, that being Springfield's one and only principle— She shall always protect her friends and those who are important to her.
data.dialogue: Commander, I'm very glad to be fighting by your side again. Is this the Elmo? I've always wanted to take a look around it.
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Oh my, do you require my assistance? Rest assured, I will not disappoint you.

data.name: Zhaohui
data.introduce: A stoic Doll with rich combat experience, she is unpretentious and decisive in action. As the leader of Monsoon Squad, she excels in combat and handling team affairs but is still a novice at lightening the mood. Don't hesitate to welcome her—a hero pursuing justice is always worthy of trust.
data.dialogue: Nice to meet you, I'm Zhaohui. Since Daiyan, Jiangyu, and Faye all call you "Commander", I guess I should too?
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Understood.

data.name: Mechty
data.introduce: A Doll who approaches everything with peak laziness—except for gaming and reading manga. She's mastered the ultimate skill: falling asleep anytime, anywhere, under any circumstance. Although she seems to embody the philosophy of "lying flat" to the extreme, she reveals her dependable side in times of crisis—though in her words, "It'd be better if we just never ran into any 'crisis' at all…"
data.dialogue: Yes, yes, it's me, the ever-patient and ever-resourceful Mechty… Commander, my luggage should have arrived before me, right?
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Eh...? I can't take a day off this time? Sure...

data.name: Klukai
data.introduce: Elegant and composed; a Doll brimming with confidence. She aspires to make every member of H.I.D.E. 404 into an elite. Only those who are familiar with her know the tenderness that lies behind her cold, strong-willed demeanor.
data.dialogue: H.I.D.E. 404's current leader, Elite Doll Klukai has arrived. It's been a while, Commander.
data.BGEOPIAGBKE: Just watch me. I'll show you how a true elite Doll perfectly completes a mission.
